Class BroadcastServiceAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.zeppelin.cluster.BroadcastServiceAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.atomix.cluster.messaging.BroadcastService

    public class BroadcastServiceAdapter
extends Object
implements io.atomix.cluster.messaging.BroadcastService
    Broadcast Service Adapter Service for broadcast messaging between nodes. The broadcast service is an unreliable broadcast messaging service backed by multicast. This service provides no guaranteed regarding reliability or order of messages.
